OL,7,FA Parc Prison inmate died aged 29
OL,8,Fafter measures to stop drugs entering
OL,9,Fthe prison in Bridgend were
OL,10,F"inadequate", an inquest has found.
OL,12,FRoss Andrew Appleby, 29, died on 18
OL,13,FJanuary 2023 at the G4S-run facility.
OL,14,FHe had been remanded at the prison in
OL,15,FOctober 2022 and was sentenced to a
OL,16,Fthree-year jail term for drug-dealing
OL,17,Foffences.
