OL,7,FA nine-day inquest into his death at
OL,8,FPontypridd Coroner's Court concluded
OL,9,Fon Thursday, 9 October, concluding
OL,10,Fthat his death was drug-related.
OL,12,FHe was found unresponsive in his cell
OL,13,Fafter exposure to synthetic cannabis
OL,14,For 'spice', the hearing was told.
OL,16,FQuestions have been raised in recent
OL,17,Fyears about the safety of prisoners at
OL,18,FParc after 17 inmates are known to
OL,19,Fhave died while behind bars in 2024.
