OL,7,FOn Tuesday, 7 October, the inquest
OL,8,Fheard how the smell of cannabis in a
OL,9,Fcorridor of the prison was so
OL,10,Fprevalent that everyone visiting
OL,11,F"passed comment on it".
OL,13,FThe jury was read an e-mail from a
OL,14,Fprison officer at Parc to a senior
OL,15,Fmanager which complained about "severe
OL,16,Fheadaches and lack of energy" while on
OL,17,Fduty, brought about, he said, by
OL,18,Fcannabis fumes on the prison's 'B'
OL,19,Fwing.
