OL,7,FAfter the inquest, a HMP Parc
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "Our thoughts
OL,9,Fremain with the family and friends of
OL,10,FMr Appleby.
OL,12,F"The prison estate is experiencing
OL,13,Fvery significant challenges related to
OL,14,Forganised crime gangs in the community.
OL,16,F"Preventing prisoners from accessing
OL,17,Fillegal drugs remains a priority at
OL,18,FParc. We have invested substantial
OL,19,Fresources into additional security
OL,20,Fstaffing, patrol dogs and drug
OL,21,Fdetection equipment.
